articles.description: Boise State (7-4, 5-2 Mountain West) at No. 22 San Diego State (10-1, 6-1, CFP No. 21), Friday at noon EST in Carson, Calif. (CBS).
articles.headline: Boise State, No. 22 SDSU meet with division titles at stake

images.name: Florida AD: Looking for sustained success in new HC
images.caption: Florida athletic director Scott Stricklin describes a lack of sustained success as one reason to let go of Dan Mullen and how that will play a factor in hiring a new head football coach.

articles.description: From Florida, LSU and USC to Washington and Virginia Tech, it promises to be a wild ride on the coaching carousel. Here's everything you need to know.
articles.headline: College football coaching carousel: Latest buzz, top candidates, analysis of every vacancy

articles.description: — The third week of October is when it could have all fallen apart at Washington State. There were easy built-in reasons and explanations if the Cougars had crumbled at that point of the season.
articles.headline: Wazzu looks to snap Apple Cup losing streak vs. Washington

images.name: The numbers behind the Ohio State and Michigan rivalry
images.caption: Chris "The Bear" Fallica crunches the numbers heading into "The Game" between Ohio State and Michigan.

articles.description: Michigan men's basketball coach Juwan Howard said he'll be at Saturday's game in Ann Arbor as the No. 5 Wolverines take on the No. 2 Ohio State Buckeyes in a matchup with serious College Football Playoff implications.
articles.headline: Michigan basketball coach Juwan Howard ready to be '12th man' for Wolverines in pivotal football matchup with Ohio State Buckeyes

articles.description: Colorado (4-7, 3-5 Pac-12) at No. 16 Utah (8-3, 7-1, No. 19 CFP), Friday at 4 p.m. EST (FOX).
articles.headline: No. 16 Utah seeking a fifth straight win over Colorado
